            At the regular meeting of the Board of Trustees of Richmond College
            appointed to be held this day = <time dateTime="1843-09-05">September 5, 1843</time> at the Second Baptist
            Church - there were present Ro. Ryland, Pres.,<aside>not a quorum</aside> J.B. Jeter, Albert Snead,
            A.G. Wortham, and A. Judson Crane - and it appearing that there was not
            a quorum of members in attendance, the members present adjourned to
            Monday evening next at 5 o'clock = A.J. Crane having been appointed
            Secretary pro tem =
          </p>
          <footer>
            <div className="signature">A. Judson Crane, Sec'y pro tempore</div>
            <div className="signature">Ro. Ryland, Pres't.</div>
          </footer>
        </section>

