            <p>Richmond, December 15th, 1846</p>
          </time>
          <p>
            At a meeting of the Trustees of Richmond College, pursuant to
            adjournment; at the Second Baptist Church -
          </p>
          <p>
            Present:  Ro. Ryland, Presd't.  J.B. Jeter, A. Hall, James Thomas,
            Ju'r., A. Thomas, and Thomas J. Evans.
          </p>
          <aside>no quorum</aside>
          <p>
            There being no quorum for business, the meeting adjourned to meet
            tomorrow evening at 1/2 past 6 o'clock at the missionary room at the
            First Baptist Church.
          </p>
          <footer>
            <div className="signature">Thos. J. Evans, Secy.</div>
