          <p>Yeas 7             Noes 4</p>
          <p>On motion the board now adjourned to meet this day week at 4 1/2 o'clock P.M.</p>
          <footer>
            <div className="signature">John M. Murray, Secretary</div>
            <div className="signature">Ro. Ryland, <u>Prest</u>.</div>
